script:
1). Where do you live?
On South 29th Street. 
It's 776-7788.
I was born in Canada.
2). Do you know when our new computers will arrive?
No, I'm not sure. 
They will come yesterday.
They came next week.
3). Why didn't you ask me before you ordered?
I'm sorry that I did.
No, you didn't ask me.
I didn't want to bother you.
